"A.P.238/4/9/12:00": "...Wait. The atmosphere's changed. There might be a powerful enemy."
"...From how long it's been, this must be the last one. Stay on your guard."
"...Of course, you were probably thinking the same thing."
"...To tell you the truth, ever since Dark Falz was revived, I've been uneasy."
"...But, fighting with you, I get the feeling that we'll manage. So, thank you."
"...Well, let's go. We need to wrap this up."
